txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Huge filth from the insects surrounding Tyrn Lhuig. Delivery of the items should be made to Othran at the base of the hilltop outpost.
'The filth left by insects can be combined with some liquids and goo to make strong adhesives. We will use what you find.'
Council of the North Task: Huge Filth
The hunters at Tyrn Lhuig expect a delivery of huge filth to be made to Othran, one of their number at the bottom of their hillside outpost.
Deliver the huge filth to Othran at Tyrn Lhuig in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver huge filth from the insects surrounding Tyrn Lhuig to Othran at the bottom of the hillside outpost.
Wanted: Huge filth from the insects surrounding Tyrn Lhuig.
